## {{ loop.index }}. {{ category.name }}

{% if category.name == "Deadlock Freedom" %}
> **Safety**: No execution can reach a state where all processes wait for conditions that will never happen.
{% elif category.name == "Liveness" %}
> **Progress**: Every action that starts must eventually complete or escalate. No infinite loops.
{% elif category.name == "Boundedness" %}
> **Resources**: No unbounded growth of state, queues, or memory. Resources are limited and monitored.
{% elif category.name == "Petri Net Analysis" %}
